# Altum_Fluctus-Theme
A theme based on the famous painting The Great Wave of Kanagawa. \
Altum Fluctus is from Latin and means deep waves, making a reference to the painting. The entire theme colorscheme is based on the colors of the _The Great Wave of Kanagawa_. \
Yet another theme with transparent elements. It's based from the _Cyperaceae_ theme from @ZB652. \
It works for both _gtk2_ and _qt(kvantum)_ theme engines. \
This theme also includes a _Konsole_ terminal theme.

